OL,3,CShould the Channel Islands compel
OL,4,Ccriminals to face victims in court?
OL,6,FIn the UK, the Victims and Courts Bill
OL,7,Fis currently being debated in the
OL,8,FHouse of Lords, where there would be a
OL,9,Frequirement for the defendant to be in
OL,10,Fthe dock.
OL,12,FIf they refused, they could face a
OL,13,Ftougher sentence or have privileges in
OL,14,Fprison taken away.
OL,16,FOne family who has pushed the UK
OL,17,Fgovernment for this new legislation in
OL,18,Fthe Victims and Courts Bill is calling
OL,19,Fit 'Olivia's Law', named after Olivia
OL,20,FPratt-Korvel, who was shot dead in
OL,21,F2022.
