OL,3,CShould the Channel Islands compel
OL,4,Ccriminals to face victims in court?
OL,6,F"It was a shock to all of us because
OL,7,Fwe weren't aware that he had a choice.
OL,9,F"I've said in the past, it's one thing
OL,10,Ffor an impact statement to be read out
OL,11,Fby court officials, it doesn't have
OL,12,Fthe same impact from coming from the
OL,13,Ffamily or the victims."
OL,15,FAntonia Elverson, Olivia's aunt,
OL,16,Fadded: "Take the choice away from him
OL,17,For her and give it to the victim and
OL,18,Fthe families; they get to make that
OL,19,Fdecision.
