OL,3,CShould the Channel Islands compel
OL,4,Ccriminals to face victims in court?
OL,6,F"We didn't get a choice as a family to
OL,7,Fgo through what we've had to go
OL,8,Fthrough. He took that away from
OL,9,Feverybody.
OL,11,F"We appreciate that a court case is a
OL,12,Fdefendant is innocent until proven
OL,13,Fguilty - it's their trial, but once
OL,14,Fthey are convicted, they shouldn't be
OL,15,Fallowed to have the opportunity (to
OL,16,Fleave)."
