OL,3,CShould the Channel Islands compel
OL,4,Ccriminals to face victims in court?
OL,6,FAntonia added that in doing their own
OL,7,Fresearch, they've found cases since
OL,8,Fthe 1980s of defendants refusing to
OL,9,Fappear in court, calling it a "long-
OL,10,Fstanding issue".
OL,12,FITV Channel's Katya Fowler reflects on
OL,13,Fher interview with Cheryl and Antonia
OL,15,FAfter we finished recording, I asked
OL,16,FOlivia's family if they would campaign
OL,17,Fin the Channel Islands for the same
OL,18,Fchange.
