OL,3,CShould the Channel Islands compel
OL,4,Ccriminals to face victims in court?
OL,6,FThey said they would, as they feel
OL,7,Fit's important for the Channel Islands
OL,8,Fto follow the UK's lead.
OL,10,FThey told me they would look into
OL,11,Fcampaigning in the New Year.
OL,13,FIn both islands, there's no legal
OL,14,Frequirement for anyone to attend their
OL,15,Fsentencing.
OL,17,FHowever, when we got in touch with the
OL,18,Fprison service in Jersey, they said
OL,19,Fthat, in rare cases, they can force a
OL,20,Fdefendant to attend court.
